article_title: Supreme Court Conservatives Split Over Antitrust Scrutiny Of State Boards

article_metadata.description: The Supreme Court's conservatives split over whether a state dental board should be blocked from keeping non-dentists out of the teeth-whitening business.
article_metadata.author: Daniel Fisher
